    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a great luster, though upon close inspection, you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all electronic features are fully functional. It\u2019s a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that\u2019s ready for the road.",
