    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride, and it's honestly been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-loved, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It runs beautifully and still looks great parked in the driveway! I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
      "price": 31500.0,
