    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-loved and meticulously maintained machine. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the slightest road-wear typical of a car that has been enjoyed responsibly. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin featuring premium leather seating that remains firm and comfortable, complemented by a fully functional infotainment suite and dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, it is in top form; the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and it has a documented history of timely oil changes and a recent comprehensive brake service. It strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability, offering a driving experience that feels tight and responsive. This car is turn-key ready for its next owner who appreciates quality and performance without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
